            <strong>Match Types:</strong>
            <ul style="margin:4px 0 0;padding-left:18px;">
                <li><code>exact</code> / <code>literal</code> &mdash; Matches the URL path exactly</li>
                <li><code>regex</code> &mdash; Uses regular expression matching (e.g., <code>/blog/(.*)</code> &rarr; <code>/content/$1</code>)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="flex:1;min-width:250px;">
            <strong>Status Codes:</strong>
            <ul style="margin:4px 0 0;padding-left:18px;">
                <li><code>301</code> &mdash; Permanent redirect (passes ~90% SEO value to target)</li>
                <li><code>302</code> &mdash; Temporary redirect (use for sales, seasonal pages)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
